      • addUITask

        public void addUITask(UITask parent,
                      UITask uiTask)
        Description copied from interface: UITaskManager
        Add a UI task to the TaskManager. If a task with the same identifier already exists, it is ignored; otherwise the task is added as a sub-task of the specified parent task. This is called by the Workspace. Calling this method does not "select" a task. That is done by calling UITaskManager.selectUITask(UITask).
        Specified by:

        Parameters:
        parent - the parent task.
